::DarkMouse::

She went to the lab and peekd in to see how things were going.
Megatron had Dracona by the throat and her feet were dangling.  
Megatron was shouting at her.  She lightly touched the side of ehr 
face and she went back to her console.  She sat downand started to 
feel sorry for Dracona.  But then she remembered that Dracona called 
her a rat.  She smiled, "Yeah, Megatron will make short work out of 
her.  That stuff I gave her will hit her like a ton of bricks.  Then 
she will tell him everything."she chuckled, "No matter how strong she 
is, she will feel very happy in a few moments."
